 
<p>
Bolsonaro has been <a href="https://www.theguardian.com/world/2022/jul/15/killing-of-lulas-party-treasurer-by-bolsonaro-supporter-raises-fears-of-violent-runup-to-brazils-election">encouraging violence</a> against his opponents and
threatening rebellion if he loses the election.  Now one of his
supporters has assassinated the treasurer of the Workers Party, which
Lula leads.

 